{"tid":709021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★降膽固醇藥、糖尿藥，如果喺街畀警察搵到，隨時被捕！","createTime":"2018-06-19T16:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T02:57:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a67ba5e938839511f3a52d8ef569e0a5f0a231","tid":709021,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"「其實除咗『偉哥』、犀利士呢啲壯陽藥，一啲常見嘅藥物，好似<span style=\"color: red;\">降膽固醇藥、糖尿藥（見表），通通都屬於第一部毒藥表列入面，如果喺街畀警察搵到，而又冇合理解釋，隨時被捕！</span>」香港藥學服務基金管理委員會成員蘇曜華指出，衞生署列為「第一部毒藥」的藥物，需要在註冊藥房，有註冊藥劑師在場監督的情況下，方可出售，市民若胡亂購買，隨時墮入法網。<br />\n<br />\n根據《藥劑業及毒藥條例》，除非得到註冊醫生或牙醫提供治療而取得第一部毒藥，否則管有該些藥物均屬違法，<span style=\"color: red;\">最高可罰款10萬元及監禁2年</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170724/photo/bkn-20170724050025113-0724_00822_001_08b.jpg?20170724083622\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170724%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170724050025113-0724_00822_001_08b.jpg%3F20170724083622&h=f8fec00d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170724/bkn-20170724050025113-0724_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170724%2Fbkn-20170724050025113-0724_00822_001.html&d=f10hdI1SAMbs4T3xEmP7B8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=86038508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170724/bkn-20170724050025113-0724_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a2bceef3d1ce891205fcd7466fe8c35a34f67914","tid":709021,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de48452888c1afe66554a85d536e5bbecd